movie.title: Child Eater
movie.description_intro: A simple night of babysitting takes a horrifying turn when Helen realizes the boogeyman really is in little Lucas' closet.
movie.description_full: A simple night of babysitting takes a horrifying turn when Helen realizes the boogeyman really is in little Lucas' closet.

movies.title: I Kill Giants
movies.summary: Twelve-year-old Barbara Thorson flees from reality, living in the imaginary world of fantasy and magic, where she fights with giants. Her family does not understand her, peers do not like her, and she irritates teachers. And only recently moved here Sofia, her same age, trying to make friends with her.

movies.title: Face of the Enemy
movies.summary: A former victim of torture attempts revenge on the Middle-Eastern woman who ruined his life many years ago. His need for vengeance is rooted in his days as a CIA agent, when he was captured by an enemy. Placed in a tiny cell and subjected to psychological and physical torture, he nonetheless refused to divulge any information. After losing everything he vows revenge on his captors.

movies.title: Terror Trap
movies.summary: While driving at night on a lonely road, the car of estranged couple Don and Nancy is hit twice by another car in the middle of nowhere. Nancy asks for help and unpleasant sheriff Cleveland offers to take them to the nearby Motel Royal Vista and wait until the morning, when their car would be towed. When the couple arrives in the low-budget motel, they are attended by a weird receptionist. They are disturbed by noises and screams from inside the next room and Don asks them to keep quiet since his wife and he are tired and need to rest. But soon they realize that they are part of a sick and deadly game, and their lives are threatened.

movies.title: Convoy
movies.summary: Lt. Cranford lives the life of a playboy sportsman until the outbreak of war when he joins the Royal Navy and is assigned to convoy protection duties. The convoy is a part of the vital supply chain that is all that is allowing Britain to fight off the Nazi threat. A German battleship targets the convoy protection ships and a deadly game of cat and mouse ensues.
